  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Create plots</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/117ebee7af7785916c2efd7f26e339ef.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/117ebee7af7785916c2efd7f26e339ef.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/117ebee7af7785916c2efd7f26e339ef.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>The basis of the game is plots. You create them and people then buy them from you to live their lives and start businesses.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the hard working ones</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/00ea088473d76e3e2a6e98de9a81a4c6.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/00ea088473d76e3e2a6e98de9a81a4c6.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/00ea088473d76e3e2a6e98de9a81a4c6.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Peoples personalities drive their behavior. Some work very hard.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And the not-so-hard working ones</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/ab66434b79f85096e66edaa0fbd2a3d8.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/ab66434b79f85096e66edaa0fbd2a3d8.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/ab66434b79f85096e66edaa0fbd2a3d8.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some are unlikely to make much money.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The happy ones</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/fd00d49436ead1fbf5942b1eb54d53d9.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/fd00d49436ead1fbf5942b1eb54d53d9.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/fd00d49436ead1fbf5942b1eb54d53d9.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some are outgoing and make a lot of friends.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >And the angry ones</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/f7992acae514c995d88a0ab582857999.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/f7992acae514c995d88a0ab582857999.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/f7992acae514c995d88a0ab582857999.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some are better at making enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >But whats this?</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/192d19c2fb2ad92aa6e9cf61490d5095.poster.avif?t=1648486330\" width=532 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/192d19c2fb2ad92aa6e9cf61490d5095.webm?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1268350/extras/192d19c2fb2ad92aa6e9cf61490d5095.mp4?t=1648486330\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Some beliefs are worse than others.",
